	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />To make a file twice as big, put this in a Windows command prompt:
<br />
<br />copy /b somefile.bin+somefile.bin doubled.bin

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
